<p begin="00:02:45.440" end="00:02:49.600" style="s2">I&#39;ve been trying to put into practice what you&#39;ve been talking about in your YouTube lectures and</p>
<p begin="00:02:50.810" end="00:02:52.520" style="s2">podcasts and and</p>
<p begin="00:02:52.520" end="00:02:56.350" style="s2">It&#39;s really helped my turn my life around. Thank you. It&#39;s like</p>
<p begin="00:02:57.140" end="00:02:59.140" style="s2">Yeah</p>
<p begin="00:02:59.690" end="00:03:01.989" style="s2">Do something you feel fragile about that</p>
<p begin="00:03:04.340" end="00:03:06.340" style="s2">Well</p>
