<p begin="00:03:30.019" end="00:03:32.289" style="s2">You know my job was threatened and</p>
<p begin="00:03:32.989" end="00:03:37.029" style="s2">quite severely, and I thought I might lose my clinical license as well and</p>
<p begin="00:03:37.720" end="00:03:39.720" style="s2">Things were up in the air in a big way.  This was over the gender pronoun usage.</p>
