<p begin="00:06:26.990" end="00:06:34.970" style="s2">I mean look I&#39;ve been protested against I watched the protesters and most of the time the vast majority of them are young people whose</p>
<p begin="00:06:35.520" end="00:06:36.840" style="s2">Whose?</p>
