<p begin="00:06:53.760" end="00:06:55.760" style="s2">need you</p>
<p begin="00:06:56.160" end="00:07:00.829" style="s2">Well first of all you know, it&#39;s not I would say it&#39;s not just young men part of that&#39;s an</p>
<p begin="00:07:00.900" end="00:07:04.310" style="s2">Artifact of the fact that most of the people who watch YouTube are young men?</p>
<p begin="00:07:05.070" end="00:07:08.749" style="s2">but but I won&#39;t evade the question I mean because</p>
<p begin="00:07:09.660" end="00:07:11.580" style="s2">See to some degree</p>
<p begin="00:07:11.580" end="00:07:17.150" style="s2">Maturation among men is a voluntary process. It&#39;s not so voluntary for women. They have to grow up fast</p>
<p begin="00:07:17.150" end="00:07:22.220" style="s2">They have a lot of things to do before they hit 30 yeah with men it can it can take longer</p>
