<p begin="00:09:44.400" end="00:09:46.429" style="s2">remarkable decline in violent crime I</p>
<p begin="00:09:46.830" end="00:09:54.109" style="s2">do think that there might be an epidemic more of aimlessness and and and depression and anxiety that sort of thing and</p>
<p begin="00:09:54.390" end="00:09:59.809" style="s2">I think that that&#39;s partly because the case for growing up is not made well</p>
<p begin="00:09:59.810" end="00:10:07.100" style="s2">And and and because we&#39;re also so cynical about our own societies. You know I was in Amsterdam month ago talking to a group of</p>
