<p begin="00:10:26.440" end="00:10:33.860" style="s2">Scrape this country out of the bottom of the ocean they built dikes to hold back the waves. It&#39;s it&#39;s free. It&#39;s it&#39;s liberal</p>
<p begin="00:10:33.860" end="00:10:39.540" style="s2">It&#39;s it&#39;s compassionate its orderly. It&#39;s beautiful. Yet they&#39;re embarrassed by it. They&#39;re embarrassed by it because of its</p>
